y:    Retaining and recruiting prominent faculty members who have a stake in the future of our communities and a passion to serve humanity.  Building a state-of-the-art research infrastructure that inspires courageous discovery and continues to attract the brightest scholars.        Read about our outstanding faculty            From the Theatre to the Hospital    Posted on April 03, 2020             Trends in 2020    Posted on March 26, 2020             Chancellor Amiridis Celebrates Donors and Advocates for Supporting UIC    Posted on April 11, 2019             Former Student and Faculty Member Inspired to Give Back    Taylor Kasper  |  Posted on March 19, 2018             UIC launches fundraising campaign to raise $750 million    Sherri McGinnis Gonzalez  |  Posted on October 30, 2017               UIC College of Engineering's first professorship in Civil and Materials Engineering empowers talented faculty    Joel Super  |  Posted on June 12, 2017             Circling Back with Gary Buslik    Taylor Kasper  |  Posted on March 15, 2017             Illinois Medicine: College of Medicine Dean Dimitri Azar, MD, MBA    Posted on February 28, 2017             Innovative Medicine: Professor K. Luan Phan, MD    Posted on February 28, 2017             Impactful Medicine: Michael Reese Professor Gail Prins, PhD ‘79    Posted on February 28, 2017                 Make Your Impact  Select a fund on our secure giving form to help empower faculty.   Give Now            IGNITE:  The Campaign for UIC    Back to main content           Give Now    IGNITE Priorities     Support Student Success    Empower Faculty    Drive Discoveries    Connect to Communities    Support A College or Unit      Understanding Giving     Giving Strategies    Gift Planning    How to Give                    UIC Logo        Advancement       Contact   601 S. Morgan Street, 2503 University Hall (MC 002), Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: 312-413-8272  advance@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitte